Text: I'd just like to point out: there is no reason to download this file. OP claims he wanted best sound possible, but take a 128kbps MP3 and turn it into a 320kbps MP3 and you've still got a 128kbps MP3 in a 320kbps wrapper. You've made a huge wav file that sounds exactly like all the other 128kbps rips out there. You can't upconvert, only down.
Uploader should try a similar trick with an out-of-focus photograph. ;)
